        <detaileddescription>
<para>For GOEP connection over RFCOMM, the reserved head room includes OBEX, RFCOMM, L2CAP and ACL headers. For GOEP connection over L2CAP, the reserved head room includes OBEX, L2CAP and ACL headers.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
